data.description: Windmill Farms residence in Choctaw Schools! 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, 2 car garage with STORM SHELTER. Open floorplan featuring raised ceilings, crown moldings, ceiling fans, etc. Spacious living room featuring fireplace, modern style full length windows with great wall space & a ceiling fan. Nice kitchen featuring a center island, stainless finished refrigerator, black gas range & dishwasher, a walk-in pantry. Large master suite with backyard outside access and also features a large bathroom area with a whirlpool tub, separate shower, double-sink vanity w/ makeup center & large walk-in closet. Large inside utility room with additional storage. Exterior features a covered front porch, a covered back patio, privacy fencing. Just 10 minutes from Tinker AFB and quick access to I-40.
